    public enum Cvv2Request
extends java.lang.Enum<Cvv2Request>
    Requests that CVV2 should be verified.
    Since:
    JSE5

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CARD_HAS_NO_CVV2
      Card holder states that the card has not CVV2 value.
      CVV2_NOT_SUBMITTED
      CVV2 value is deliberately bypassed or is not provided by the merchant.
      CVV2_PRESENT
      Card holder states that the CVV2 value is present on the card and can be verified.
      CVV2_PRESENT_BUT_ILLEGIBLE
      Card holder states that the CVV2 value is present on the card but it is illegible.
